query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS integration_setup_packets (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  customerId INT,
  intakeId INT,
  suiteApplicationId INT,
  sourceType ENUM('suite_application', 'intake') NOT NULL,
  integration ENUM('google_business', 'meta', 'quickbooks') NOT NULL,
  status ENUM('ready', 'in_progress', 'connected', 'blocked') DEFAULT 'ready' NOT NULL,
  packetVersion VARCHAR(16) DEFAULT 'v1.0.0' NOT NULL,
  packetJson JSON NOT NULL,
  generatedFrom JSON,
  lastOpenedAt TIMESTAMP NULL,
  connectedAt TIMESTAMP NULL,
  notes TEXT,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);
